description:
John F. Kennedy stood by the separation of church and state. According to Bible prophecy, however, the separation of church and state, along with religious liberty, will come to an end in America. In this presentation, Walter Veith explains how Hegelian dialectic is at work to accomplish the aims of Revelation 13’s first beast. He looks at how various elements are working together to fulfill the prophetic scenarios that will be in place at the time of Christ’s return. 

What role do crises play in fulfilling prophecy? What is significant about the fact that American presidents can trace their bloodlines back to Charlemagne, who was crowned Holy Roman Emperor by the Pope?  Who are Trump’s evangelical advisors and what is their relationship with the papacy? How is the Pope involved with the US? 

This presentation looks at fascinating facts surrounding the election of Donald Trump as president, including: Obama’s liberal legacy, The Simpsons’ predictions, and relationships between Trump’s administration and Kenneth Copeland, the archbishop of New York, and the Pope. Has the election of Donald Trump brought us any closer to the fulfilment of end time prophecy? Find out in this fascinating presentation.

Discover more: http://amazingdiscoveries.org/
